  <data name="AboutPage_Description.Text" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Welcome to Live Photo Box! This professional yet easy-to-use Live Photo processing tool is designed to effortlessly break the ecosystem barriers between Apple and Android. It losslessly converts Live Photos shot on iPhone into formats natively supported by Google Photos. By perfectly preserving the original video quality and dynamic frame rates, it ensures your vivid memories are flawlessly presented across any platform.

Beyond ultimate format conversion, the software offers a suite of powerful local processing capabilities. You can "unbind" Live Photos with a single click, splitting them into high-quality static images and independent video files. For selfies taken with the front camera, it intelligently analyzes the underlying video data to accurately identify and fix mirror inversion issues. Coupled with a highly efficient concurrent batch processing engine, even massive photo collections can be handled at once with ease.

Click the [Batch Convert], [Extract &amp; Split], or [Repair Tool] buttons on the page to start your processing journey right now!</value>
  </data>
